description:
This archive contains the data produced after the bioinformatic analysis for the study "The Role of Ciliary Function in Airway Epithelial Defense against&nbsp; Pseudomonas aeruginosa ".&nbsp; 
 In particular, it contains the following files: 

  salmon.merged.gene_counts.tsv &nbsp; Raw counts from Salmon v1.10.0&nbsp; produced as output after running&nbsp; the nf-core RNA-seq pipeline version 3.10.1. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 
  hAO_inf_hAO_ctrl_IHWsigFCgenes.xlsx&nbsp; Differentially expressed genes produced using Bioconductor package DESeq2 v1.38.3.&nbsp;

